{"tid":1984943,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愛的迫降真人版金正藍長子金韓松","createTime":"2020-04-22T20:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T05:32:55.000Z","uid":124372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39795eead9d35a5afbee138b8f260e13f7826c1e","tid":1984943,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T20:05:49.000Z","msg":"現在金正恩都應該就快死<br />\n金韓松到底可唔可以返朝鮮繼位呢<br />\n佢熱愛民主自由被CIA保護<br />\n佢繼位朝鮮將會變天<br />\n但班朝鮮老屎忽會罷手嗎<br />\n而南韓青瓦台根本唔想統一<br />\n如果你認為南韓係想南北韓統一<br />\n只能說少年你太年輕了<br />\n除了政治係眾人之事<br />\n經濟亦然<br />\n統一將會令南韓出現二十年的經濟衰退<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oxc0KYe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foxc0KYe.jpg&h=380670af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b13a79c6c68acb9ddc7c07b2dd8c0313203f01b9","tid":1984943,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef10fc1f46a0aed78943cadd58eb3a5e05505685","tid":1984943,"uid":41484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"金正男原來有仔，宜家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}